data.description: Assumable low interest VA loan. Ask your agent. Fabulous Ashland Ranch home with a major remodel just completed about 18 months ago . A must see home with the latest detailed finishes New off white cabinets and quarts countertops make the kitchen stand out like no other. Tiled lighted backsplashes and complete tile surrounding the center island.  Bosch oven and dishwasher along with a hidden cabinet microwave. The master bath features a free standing tub. rain head shower with two sprays. Electric fireplace. Designer lights and wallpaper in just the right places. Lots of extra shelving in the closets including a elevated rack for additional storage. A split floor plan offer a lot of privacy.
